  <description>
    <p>
      Editor features:
      <ul>
        <li>Multiple buffers/tabs</li>
        <li>Unlimited undo/redo</li>
        <li>Regex search and replace</li>
        <li>Syntax highlighting</li>
        <li>Customizable color schemes (including 24-bit RGB)</li>
        <li>Customizable key bindings</li>
        <li>Command language with auto-completion</li>
        <li>Unicode 14 compatible text rendering</li>
        <li>Support for all xterm key combos</li>
        <li>Support for kitty's keyboard protocol</li>
        <li>Support for multiple encodings (using iconv)</li>
        <li>Jump to definition (using ctags)</li>
        <li>Jump to compiler error</li>
        <li>Copy to system clipboard (using OSC 52, which works over SSH)</li>
        <li>EditorConfig support</li>
      </ul>
    </p>
  </description>
